room_title: Escape room "Escape the Subway" by Escape Room Clearwater Beach in Tampa
room_description:
Visiting friends in the city, you decide to jump on the subway to head downtown. As you're sitting on the subway, you hear an MTA message come over the speakers: â€œAttention, a malfunction has occurred involving the trains brake system." 
Work together to figure out the clues to get the emergency brakes back on line before you hit the end of the line. Gather clues, solve puzzles, combine information, decipher secret meanings and trigger hidden mechanisms to stop a runaway subway.
